About:
In April 2014 REALTIME had a live gig in a little pub very close to the Cologne Cathedral. They surprised their audience not only with new interpretations of songs from former albums, but as well some new, so far unreleases tracks. The concert was recorded in a nice quality and this album is the result.

released 27 July 2014

Thomas Bock: synths, programming and keys
Norbert Hensellek: synths, programming and keys

All tracks composed by Thomas Bock

Recorded live and direct on 26th of April 2014 at the "Dominikaner", Cologne, Germany

Mastered by Thomas Bock & Norbert Hensellek in Cologne, June 2014
